//]]>
</script></div>
</div>
</div>
<p><br /></p>
<p>恋喜欢画画，但是总是画的不好看。</p>
<p>恋喜欢别人给她画画。</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">大家给恋画的画</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">谢谢大家欸</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content"><script type="text/javascript" src="http://d3g0gp89917ko0.cloudfront.net/v--3e3a6f7dbcc9/common--javascript/yahooui/tabview-min.js">
</script>
