</ul>
<div class="yui-content">
<div id="wiki-tab-0-0"><img src="http://scpsandboxcn.wikidot.com/local--files/breaddddd3/img097.jpg" alt="img097.jpg" class="image" /><br />
来自面包<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/breaddddd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3471238); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3471238&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610201774" alt="breaddddd" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3471238)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/breaddddd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3471238); return false;">breaddddd</a></span></div>
